channel.title: Help with portforwarding, and a big reward too!

This is what it asks him to enter, and I need to know, what does he need to enter in these...

What should he enter in these? PM Me please. I probably will lose this topic. Thanks.
EDIT: Should he enter, Port Start: 43594 Port Ends: 43594 Port Map: 1
